FBIS4-52440 "dreas090_c_94037" FBIS-EAS-94-090 Daily Report 8 May 1994 North Korea Kim Chong-il Receives Gift From Widow of `Martyr' Kim Chong-il Receives Gift From Widow of `Martyr' SK0805085794 Pyongyang KCNA in English 0813 GMT 8 May 94 SK0805085794 Pyongyang KCNA English BFN [Text] Pyongyang, May 8 (KCNA) -- The dear leader Comrade Kim Chong-il received a gift from the visiting Chinese woman involved in the anti-Japanese revolutionary struggle Hu Zhenyi, widow of Chai Shirong, a Chinese anti-Japanese revolutionary martyr, and her family members. The gift was handed to an official concerned.
